const PhoneNumber = (props) => {

  // console.log("props.value",props.value)

  useEffect(() => {
    if (props.value && props.value !== 'undefined') {
      const number = props.value.split(' ')
      const code = number[0]
      const phone_ = number[1]

      if (code) {
        setSelectedCountry(countryCodes.find(item => item.dial_code === code))
        setPhone(phone_)
      }
      else {
        setPhone(code)
      }
    }
  }, [])
  const [selectedCountry, setSelectedCountry] = useState(countryCodes[0]);
  const [phone, setPhone] = useState(null);

  const handleCountryChange = (e) => {
    const code = e.target.value;
    const country = countryCodes.find((c) => c.code === code);
    setSelectedCountry(country);
  };
  useEffect(() => {
    props.onChange({ name: props.name, target: { value: phone ? `${selectedCountry.dial_code} ${phone}` : "" }, })
  }, [selectedCountry, phone])
  // console.log("selectedCountry", selectedCountry)
  return (
    <div style={{ display: "flex", marginTop: "1px" }}>
      <div>
        <select style={{ height: "2.4rem", width: "100%", border: "1px solid lightgray" }} value={selectedCountry.code} onChange={handleCountryChange}>
          {countryCodes.map((c) => (
            <option key={c.code} value={c.code}>
              {c.flag} ({c.dial_code})
            </option>
          ))}
        </select>
      </div>
      {/* <input type="text" placeholder="Phone number" /> */}
      <div style={{ width: "100%" }}>
        
        <Input
          style={props.style ? props.style : { "width": "100%" }}
          // style={{width:"100%"}}
          size={"large"}
          name={props.name}
          onChange={e => {
            const result = e.target.value.replace(/\D/g, '');
            setPhone(result)
            // const regex = /^[0-9\b]+$/;
            // if (e.target.value === "" || regex.test(e.target.value)) {
            //   // setVal(e.target.value);
            //   setPhone(e.target.value)
            // }
          }}
          // onChange={e => setPhone(e.target.value)}
          disabled={props.disabled}
          className={props.className}
          value={phone}
          onKeyPress={props.onKeyPress}
          type="text"
          // pattern="[0-9]*"
        // id="phone"
        // type="text"
        // placeholder="Phone"
        // name="phone"
        ></Input>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};

export default PhoneNumber;
